{"tid":92983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有錢買房買車就是欠錢不還，一家7口被滅門！】","createTime":"2017-01-24T04:51:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T06:22:15.000Z","uid":28765,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a1b2eb7d8585df98722ef12ed80292fc3c029e5e","tid":92983,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T04:51:45.000Z","msg":"河北保定村民龐小龍一家三代同時被殺死，包括死者的妻子和母親、兩個兒子、一個姐姐、一個妹妹。<br />\n<br />\n兇手殺人後萬念俱灰，衝到馬路上，被大車當場撞死。到底是什麼深仇大恨，讓兇手痛下殺手？<br />\n<br />\n到底是什麼深仇大恨，讓兇手如此悲情地結束自己的生命？<br />\n<br />\n原來，兇手借給龐小龍十多萬元，多次多年討要不還。但龐小龍的大兒子卻買車買房，即將舉行婚禮。<br />\n<br />\n兇手無論如何也想不通：&ldquo;有錢買車買房，為何不還錢？！&rdquo;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f47542f55d5c249ca5a62516eae69f635cacf727","tid":92983,"uid":4326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T04:55:44.000Z","msg":"抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba1c5f11d59905f3ce593a2bbb998eef2f46cc1","tid":92983,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T04:56:57.000Z","msg":"又死8隻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9caa9130cfa47ec8ed12456880e29b9fa5346551","tid":92983,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T04:57:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ed72901dab07d7d6288af3cea35c6b2afdd403","tid":92983,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T04:59:32.000Z","msg":"我係佢，會殺剩龐小龍"},{"pid":"3306afb